- **< 0Â°C** â†’ Blinking **Blue** (Freezing)
- **0â€“8Â°C** â†’ **Cyan** (Cold)
- **8â€“16Â°C** â†’ **Green** (Mild)
- **16â€“24Â°C** â†’ **Yellow** (Comfortable)
- **24â€“32Â°C** â†’ **Orange** (Warm)
